    "description": "Crystal guardians is a rogue-like tower defense game where you need to defend your base crystal on an expanding procedural generated battlefield. Gain a strategic advantage using the many towers + crystal combinations and unique item combinations stored in those towers. Make use of the expanding battlefield by placing towers on strategic position for maximal damage to the enemies.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Loads of unique tower loadout combinations to be made<br></li><li> Currently over 100 items available<br></li><li> 36 tower combinations<br></li><li> Extensive meta progression<br></li><li> 10 unique boss rounds<br></li><li> Loads of different enemies<br></li><li> Unique rounds<br></li><li> Procedural generated levels, every run is different </li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend your base in this challenging tower defense</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322090/extras/0e03a43a611503f93f083dd3c475fc40.poster.avif?t=1743810444\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322090/extras/0e03a43a611503f93f083dd3c475fc40.webm?t=1743810444\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322090/extras/0e03a43a611503f93f083dd3c475fc40.mp4?t=1743810444\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build the perfect loadouts on towers</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322090/extras/5b936e9bf0c4997494fed5519356ad2c.poster.avif?t=1743810444\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2322090/extras/5b936e9bf0c4997494fed5519356ad2c.webm?t=1743810444\" type=\"video/we